{"tid":110042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友話要上同學屋企做project,但groupmate全部都係男人","createTime":"2017-02-06T11:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T03:09:28.000Z","uid":48631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8dc76019d14afa53739ded978fdfb42cb2851f","tid":110042,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"我一聽到佢話groupmate全部都係男人即刻嚇親,梗係同佢講唔撚得,咁佢問我份project點算好,我話我同佢一齊上去做,而家上左個條友屋企<br />\n好彩個3條友都係毒撚樣(一個肥毒,另一個東菇頭,仲有一個樣都算人樣,但係講野口窒窒唔敢望人)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw,我而家一路坐左喺張梳化度打邊打PS4,一邊上連登,一邊監視佢地,而佢地4個就坐左喺飯台做緊project<br />\n我女友好認真上網搵緊資料,個3條毒撚就扮做project但時不時偷望我條女,仲要有條友特登對住我條女搞埋晒d冇人識笑既gag,我條女完全畀唔到反應佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢地好似想食左我條女咁既樣就好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c568fe9d6a18bd0a9b8afdac16121d682c8fa414","tid":110042,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/195505_82eeb3901bf848aa079c595143bd432f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F195505_82eeb3901bf848aa079c595143bd432f.jpg&h=6eb5e162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你比人帽咗幾多次"},{"pid":"7b553404249304e58fe89a79a7332d447d0fc25a","tid":110042,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">帽事嘅，你多疑啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b15e4c60d6da4e25c6458ea9f16d09d12e490f0","tid":110042,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/195505_82eeb3901bf848aa079c5951